::Shadow Wing::

"I'll go and put the scanner away then."
She turned and walked down the hall. And Shadow Wing is a dumb name 
for an owl too, she thought.  She felt so sure he would be happy 
about the idea of her changing forms for him.  Now he almost seamed 
mad at her for coming up with the idea.  She shook her head and tried 
not to think about it.

She put the scanner back and went back to the engine room.

> Wing. "Next time you plan a stunt like this ask me first."
